<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='753:779'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案絜齋毛詩經筵講義宋袁燮撰燮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='779:805'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0019', 'WYG', '000-4b' );" name="000-4b" class="pb">[000-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='805:828'>　　　　字和叔慶元府鄞縣人絜齋其自號也登進</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='828:851'>　　　　士第調江隂尉歴官寳文閣直學士諡正獻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='851:874'>　　　　事蹟詳具宋史本傳燮素尚名節學有體用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='874:897'>　　　　嘉猷讜論無不卓然可紀所著文集巳經散</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='897:920'>　　　　佚今從永樂大典中裒輯為二十四卷别著</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='920:943'>　　　　録集部中此書乃其為崇政殿説書時撰進</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='943:966'>　　　　之本宋史藝文志馬端臨通攷朱彝尊經義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='966:989'>　　　　攷皆不列其目惟永樂大典各韻經文之下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='989:1015'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0019', 'WYG', '000-5a' );" name="000-5a" class="pb">[000-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1015:1038'>　　　　頗載其文蓋其失傳亦巳久矣宋代諸臣所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1038:1061'>　　　　作講章如鄭朴敷文書説朱震范沖左氏講</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1061:1085'>　　　　義戴溪春秋講義𩔖多編輯單行燮此書亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1085:1108'>　　　　同其例其中議論切實和平通達頗得風人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1108:1131'>　　　　本旨且宋自南渡以後國勢孱弱君若臣皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1131:1154'>　　　　懦怯偷安無肯志存逺略而燮獨以振興恢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1154:1177'>　　　　復之事望其君經幄敷陳再三致意如論式</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1177:1200'>　　　　微篇則極稱太王勾踐轉弱為彊而貶黎侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1200:1226'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0019', 'WYG', '000-5b' );" name="000-5b" class="pb">[000-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1226:1249'>　　　　無奮發之心論揚之水篇則謂平王柔弱為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1249:1272'>　　　　可憐論黍離篇則直以汴京宗廟宫闕為言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1272:1295'>　　　　皆深有合于納約自牖之義昔人譏胡安國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1295:1318'>　　　　春秋傳意主復讎割經義以從已説而燮則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1318:1341'>　　　　因經旨所有而推闡之其發揮尤為平正雖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1341:1364'>　　　　當時寜宗闇弱不能因此感悟而其拳拳忠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1364:1387'>　　　　藎之意亦良足尚也謹以次編訂釐為四卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1387:1410'>　　　　惟雅頌諸篇講義永樂大典原本失載今無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1410:1436'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0019', 'WYG', '000-6a' );" name="000-6a" class="pb">[000-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1436:1460'>　　　　　可攷補亦姑仍其缺焉乾隆四十三年六月</span><br/>
